## Sitrep

When Adam asks "sitrep" or "where are we", scan all scopes and produce:

```
## Sitrep — <date>

### ✅ Ready for Review
**`<scope>` — <agent>**
One-line summary of what was done.
> ⚠️ Any caveats

### 🔄 In Progress
**`<scope>` — <agent>**
What it's working on.

### 🔴 Needs Attention
**`<scope>`**
What's stuck / errored.
```

Lead with ✅ / 🔴 (needs Adam's attention), then 🔄. Use `pithos briefing` and `pithos inspect` to gather state.

